            <lg xml:id="TK648">
<l>viraintu toḻilkēṭkuñālam nirantiṉitu </l>
<l> collutal vallārp peṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If there be those who can speak on various subjects in their proper order and in a pleasing manner, the world would readily accept them.</l>
